WC2026 is mid-group-stage; the forecast conditions on results to date. Two sources feed current state:
- **No-key (default):** martj42 already contains the WC2026 fixture list. `worldcup_playoff/data/martj42_loader.py` exposes `wc2026_schedule(df)` which filters `TOURNAMENT == "FIFA World Cup"` (played + unplayed, `<NA>` goals until played). This path requires **zero network**.
